•ACI 211:Standard Practice for SelectingProportions for Normal, Heavyweight, and Mass Concrete
•ACI 318: Building Code Requirements for Structural Concrete
•ASTM C94: Standard Specification for Ready-Mixed Concrete
•CSI MasterFormat Division 03-30-00: Cast-in-Place Concrete
•UNSPSC Code 30111500: Ready Mix
